Honey, I'm a homeowner✨ Well it happened. I bought my dream home. And not just any dream home. I bought my dream three-story Victorian home (four stories if you count the basement that I'm turning into a gym). I've been manifesting this home for the last few years, and it's finally mine. I've always wanted an older home that I could restore and fill with angelic details✨Grateful is a massive understatement for what I’m feeling this week. I’ve had so many dreams this year, and they’re all coming true✨🕊️ Stay magical and open; you never know what will come your way. "What if it doesn't come true? Ah, but what if it does?"🐇
